</td></tr><tr><td>
<italic>&#x0201c;It was hard to get people on. &#x02026; they know there is a stop smoking course, and they will come because they want to stop smoking today, but I don&#x02019;t think a lot of people wake up saying, &#x0201c;I want to cut down&#x02026;I did ask people, even the people that came in&#x02026; &#x0201c;Oh, I want to stop smoking&#x0201d; I&#x02019;d tell them that we were doing the reduction or to stop smoking and they say, &#x0201c;I want to stop smoking, not the reduction.&#x0201d; PH04</italic>
