<italic>&#x0201c;During the period that it was running we actually managed to recruit about ten people into the stop smoking service, but when I offered&#x02026; those same people the choice of joining the Redpharm study, they all declined and the reason they declined was because when they were given the choice about being supported or not supported, they didn&#x02019;t want to take the risk, of being not supported.&#x0201d; PH06</italic>
